    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/aa109ed1ecf2e3dbd320667c94a533a1.poster.avif?t=1764891899\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/aa109ed1ecf2e3dbd320667c94a533a1.webm?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/aa109ed1ecf2e3dbd320667c94a533a1.mp4?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Six Days in Fallujah》是一款第一人称战术射击游戏。本作将带你投身近乎真实的城市战场，你需要掌握现实世界中的各种战术技巧才能攻克难关。在单人游戏中领导AI火力小组，或与其他玩家进行在线合作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏的制作得到了数十位陆战队员和陆军士兵的帮助。这些战士都曾亲历现代战争史上数一数二的惨烈战斗，而在他们指点下制作的巷战场面也充满了仿佛历史事件般的真实感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/9cb1c134fda4ad8ffe08e92e6a8331d4.avif?t=1764891899\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras_big/9cb1c134fda4ad8ffe08e92e6a8331d4.avif?t=1764891899 width=800 height=185 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>领导AI火力小组</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/fc3221813b57f49dbf707b0d89468cb9.poster.avif?t=1764891899\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/fc3221813b57f49dbf707b0d89468cb9.webm?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/fc3221813b57f49dbf707b0d89468cb9.mp4?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为捍卫而生,为胜利而战。你的AI火力小队会自动使用真实的海军陆战队战术保护你。但在复杂情况下,他们需要你的指挥。下达命令让小队压制敌人、突入工事、防守阵地、保护目标,等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>4人在线合作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/36038f12958084130c468cda0df4d0ea.poster.avif?t=1764891899\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/36038f12958084130c468cda0df4d0ea.webm?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/36038f12958084130c468cda0df4d0ea.mp4?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >紧密合作！团队协同在本游戏中至关重要。AI敌人会对你展开跟踪、包抄、埋伏，还会借助隧道发动偷袭，以及引诱你进入陷阱。它们使用的战术与第二次费卢杰之战时的那些一般无二，也正是这些战术让那场战斗成为了半个世纪以来最血腥的一战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以与好友一起游玩、使用在线匹配，或是与真人和AI队友混编的六人小队进行游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>2个故事任务 + 8个生成式任务</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/9ea431e380e616209de26bcab0b14b29.poster.avif?t=1764891899\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/9ea431e380e616209de26bcab0b14b29.webm?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/9ea431e380e616209de26bcab0b14b29.mp4?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏讲述的真实故事比虚构更加惊悚，它将通过还原历史、真正的战斗录像以及亲历者的讲述，带你深入ISIS崛起的时代。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Six Days in Fallujah》目前包含最初的两个故事任务、一个新的生成式任务和七个更新过的生成式任务。每个生成式任务都可以单人游玩，或是与真人和AI队友组成混编小队进行游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>生成式关卡构建</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/5fa3b6881b255a0ea320ad5d70f06703.poster.avif?t=1764891899\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/5fa3b6881b255a0ea320ad5d70f06703.webm?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/5fa3b6881b255a0ea320ad5d70f06703.mp4?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >陆战队员永远不知道下一扇门后会出现什么，因此你也不知道。每当你开启一个任务，建筑的内外布局都会完全改变，敌人会占据</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新的位置，每次出现的威胁都将独一无二。你永远不知道接下来会面对什么——真实的战场也同样如此。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全方位沙盒</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/2e7feb4dd87e0966b8cf050fd58ddd40.poster.avif?t=1764891899\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/2e7feb4dd87e0966b8cf050fd58ddd40.webm?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/2e7feb4dd87e0966b8cf050fd58ddd40.mp4?t=1764891899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Six Days in Fallujah》中不存在所谓的“前线”或“边界”。敌人会对你展开跟踪、包抄、埋伏，还会将你引向无处不在的陷阱。他们会从任何方向发动攻击，无论室内还是室外。爬上屋顶、翻越窗户，穿过窄道。一切都由你来决定。而后果也将由你承担。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>第二次费卢杰之战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/e4ccfbceb69c56c782959323e8734b3a.avif?t=1764891899\" width=616 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2004年，基地组织在伊拉克夺取了费卢杰市的控制权。他们以此为基地，残忍对待当地居民，发动跨地区的恐怖袭击。整整六个月后，伊拉克总理下令所有平民离开这座城市，以便伊拉克、美国和英国军队发起联合行动，夺回费卢杰。而这场第二次费卢杰之战仅仅用了六天时间，就跻身半个世纪以来最惨烈的战役。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>路线图</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548850/extras/3b40bb4244b88bb2d3f3947292d22268.avif?t=1764891899\" width=616 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Six Days》目前提供 2 个故事任务，外加 8 个程序任务，这些任务设置在每次玩游戏时程序生成的城市地图中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们计划在游戏全面发布时发布另外 12 个任务以及各种新功能。这些内容将免费提供给抢先体验用户，在添加更多内容后，新购买者的价格可能会在未来上涨。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们目前的目标是在 2026 年底全面发布。</p>",
